:warning: Support for this device is experimental. :warning:

Compile Tasmota 8.3.1.6+ with following options:

```
#define USE_ZIGBEE
#undef USE_ZIGBEE_ZNP
#define USE_ZIGBEE_EZSP
```

This device requires serial flashing using the TX/RX/IO0 pads.

It also requires flashing the EFR32 device with EmberZNet Pro firmware (procedure still under work).